'''Dnalvec''' was the main port [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Sriluur/Legends|Sriluur]], which housed three of the four main [[Spaceport/Legends|spaceports]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]]. It was a chaotic frontier environment of drifting star [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]], information merchants, and [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]].

It was home to the [[Weequay/Legends|Weequay's]] [[Dnalvec Militia]].<ref name="air">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref> The [[Houk Territories]] were located less than 30 kilometers to the north, and there was a substantial [[Houk/Legends|Houk]] population in the city.

The [[Boneglass Canyon]] connected it to the northern edge of the [[Copper Coast]] twenty-five [[Kilometer/Legends|kilometers]] away.

